        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[抓狂]#昨晚失眠可能是节后综合征#】节后综合征是指节假日结束之后，大家重新适应工作或学习环境时可能出现的心理和生理状态。#节后综合征有哪些症状# [疑问]...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抓狂]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%98%A8%E6%99%9A%E5%A4%B1%E7%9C%A0%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E8%8A%82%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%BE%81%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%98%A8%E6%99%9A%E5%A4%B1%E7%9C%A0%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E8%8A%82%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%BE%81%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#昨晚失眠可能是节后综合征#</span></a>】节后综合征是指节假日结束之后，大家重新适应工作或学习环境时可能出现的心理和生理状态。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%8A%82%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%BE%81%E6%9C%89%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%8A%82%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%BE%81%E6%9C%89%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#节后综合征有哪些症状#</span></a> <span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>？躯体上主要表现为疲倦、失眠、昏昏欲睡、不正常的肌肉酸痛、胃口欠佳等；精神上主要表现为难以集中精神工作、焦虑、容易发怒等。节后综合征经常发生在长假期后，春节假期结束后尤其明显。大家中招了吗<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%E8%AF%B4%E4%B8%8A%E7%8F%AD%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B2%E6%B4%BB%E5%84%BF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%E8%AF%B4%E4%B8%8A%E7%8F%AD%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B2%E6%B4%BB%E5%84%BF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#专家说上班第一天少干活儿#</span></a>  （央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6YXeAFH" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 07:27:38 GMT</pubDate>
